                                .usage-card__main 
                                    a(href="#").usage-card__download.download-btn.download-btn--violet Скачать бесплатно
                                .usage-card__description 
                                    span.accent-text Скачайте программу 
                                    .usage-card__description-space
                                    span.usage-card__description-text на свой ПК или ноутбук
                            .everyday__usage-card.usage-card 
                                .usage-card__title.accent-text Шаг 2.
                                .usage-card__main 
